nodes.text: Forch Gomou was a reactor tender working in 22 BBY on Coruscant. He wore a Burgundy Bodysuit. Gomou was a patron in the Outlander Club, in the Uscru Entertainment District, in the last years of the Galactic Republic. Gomou had black hair and brown eyes.
Gomou's name is already known from the original Official Star Wars Fact Files, but did not get a face until 2017.
